15:T436,Internal evidence clearly identifies this as a stemmed tibial baseplate for the PCK revision knee system. Division (Joint Replacement) and category (Knee Tibial Components) are consistent. Specifications indicate 8 sizes with defined AP/ML dimensions and compatibility with stem extensions and offset junctions, typical of modular revision components. Entity type is product_family as this represents a line of stemmed baseplates in multiple sizes. However, critical gaps exist: (1) Brand field is empty - unclear if PCK is the brand or a product code; (2) No material specification provided - tibial baseplates are typically titanium alloy or cobalt-chromium; (3) No external verification possible; (4) PCK system identity cannot be confirmed without manufacturer documentation. Confidence set to 0.75 due to clear internal consistency but lack of verification. Review required to: confirm PCK brand/system identity, verify material composition, validate size matrix, and ensure this should remain a standalone product family vs. being grouped with other PCK tibial components.7:["$","div",null,{"className":"min-h-screen bg-[#0A0A0A] text-white","children":[["$","script",null,{"type":"application/ld+json","dangerouslySetInnerHTML":{"__html":"{\"@context\":\"https://schema.org/\",\"@type\":\"Product\",\"name\":\"PCK Stemmed Tibial Base Plate\",\"description\":\"Stemmed tibial base plate for PCK revision knee system with enhanced fixation\",\"brand\":{\"@type\":\"Brand\",\"name\":\"Meril\"},\"category\":\"Knee Tibial Components\",\"manufacturer\":{\"@type\":\"Organization\",\"name\":\"Meril Life Sciences\"},\"offers\":{\"@type\":\"AggregateOffer\",\"offerCount\":\"1\",\"lowPrice\":\"0\",\"priceCurrency\":\"INR\",\"availability\":\"https://schema.org/InStock\"}}"}}],["$","div",null,{"className":"max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12 md:py-24","children":[["$","nav",null,{"className":"flex mb-10 text-sm text-muted-foreground","aria-label":"Breadcrumb","children":[["$","$